Class DataProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.weltraumschaf.juberblog.cmd.publish.DataProcessor

  •  class DataProcessor
extends Object
    Processes a data file. Processing includes:
    • meta data processing
    • headline extraction
    • slug generation
    • format HTML
    Author:
    Sven Strittmatter
